The 2015 Conference on Retroviruses and Opportunistic Infections included new 
and exciting advances in the realm of antiretroviral therapy. The Temprano trial 
demonstrated benefits from early antiretroviral therapy and isoniazid preventive 
therapy. Important data on investigational antiretroviral drugs were presented, 
