A cluster-randomised controlled trial to assess the effectiveness and 
cost-effectiveness of a childhood obesity prevention programme delivered through 
schools, targeting 6-7 year old children: the WAVES study protocol.

Adab P(1), Pallan MJ(2), Lancashire ER(3), Hemming K(4), Frew E(5), Griffin 
